  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> Strike</p>\n<hr />\n<p>This tightly sealed metal container is filled with highly pressurized gas that can explode to release a powerful shockwave. A pressure bomb deals @Damage[4d4[bludgeoning]] damage and [[/r (4[splash])[bludgeoning]]]{4 bludgeoning splash damage}. On a critical hit, the target is knocked @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.j91X7x0XSomq8d60]{Prone}.</p>\n<p>Medium or smaller creatures who take splash damage are pushed 5 feet away from the target, and then, if the target is Large or smaller, it is pushed 5 feet away from you.</p>\n<p>You gain a +3 item bonus to attack rolls.</p>"
